{"tid":1769551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被修例風波牽動情緒 記者半年懼卧床 主婦胃痛不止","createTime":"2019-12-05T03:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T07:53:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"42d8929f52ea9c245653ed94c3d54169fe8c7c96","tid":1769551,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"反修例示威持續已半年，在示威現場採訪的記者及觀看新聞直播的市民，部分人身體及情緒分別受到不同程度的影響。經常在示威現場採訪及直播的立場新聞記者陳朗昇表示，回家後發現情緒出現問題，最深刻是6.12當日目擊示威者中槍倒地後，當晚發惡夢，過去半年甚至不敢在床上而要在梳化上睡覺。<br />\n<br />\n家庭主婦阿娟表示，看到7.21元朗襲擊事件的新聞後，整晚不停流淚，之後一度暫停觀看新聞直播，情緒稍有好轉，但中大及理大事件期間，再觀看直播後，發現生理反應更大，胃痛不止。<br />\n<br />\n香港紅十字會表示，由6月至今，透過熱線、現場及預約輔導服務，接觸超過1400名香港市民，當中有家長、前線示威者、社工、警察和警察家屬等，求助人士當中，約7%人有傷害自己或他人傾向，他們大部分本身亦是有情緒問題人士。<br />\n<br />\n紅十字會指出，示威活動持續半年，一般市民的情緒都會被牽動，在7.21元朗襲擊事件，及11月11日西灣河開槍事件後，致電求助熱線的市民亦特別多，提醒市民多留意自己及家人的情緒表現及精神狀況，如果發現情緒問題影響日常工作，最好找專家評估或者多參與活動減壓，平衡心理。<br />\n<br />\n有社工自發組織「心聆樹窿」的義工團隊，透過「擺街站」及利用Telegram網上頻道，為市民提供支援，他認為透過「面對面」對話，能協助求助者消減負面情緒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FvdwXQWc1GC11No6hA8AsQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-12/a7e9e3a0-1705-11ea-bfe6-fbd382d375cc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFvdwXQWc1GC11No6hA8AsQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2Fa7e9e3a0-1705-11ea-bfe6-fbd382d375cc&h=43b99350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立場新聞記者陳朗昇表示，採訪6.12示威後曾發惡夢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A2%AB%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E7%89%BD%E5%8B%95%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%87%BC%E5%8D%A7%E5%BA%8A-%E4%B8%BB%E5%A9%A6%E8%83%83%E7%97%9B%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A2-015453623.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%2589%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%2592-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2587%25BC%25E5%258D%25A7%25E5%25BA%258A-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E8%2583%2583%25E7%2597%259B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A2-015453623.html&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=f809daf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A2%AB%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E7%89%BD%E5%8B%95%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%87%BC%E5%8D%A7%E5%BA%8A-%E4%B8%BB%E5%A9%A6%E8%83%83%E7%97%9B%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A2-015453623.html</a>"},{"pid":"e6a39543454e6c135caebc0c37463770c490032f","tid":1769551,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"英國美國加拿大都攻擊緊中國<br />\n但啲tweets無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Rt + like + reply</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=4286eb19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task2</span></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"57ae9eca23c48def99a7cc53a700369755d5ae97","tid":1769551,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"正常香港人都會"},{"pid":"970f3db8d9e6e570c697b574cdd573be0821420d","tid":1769551,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57ae9eca23c48def99a7cc53a700369755d5ae97","tid":1769551,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"正常香港人都會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n想有正常生活同心情都咁困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor